PrecisRegulations Amending the FIREARMS FEES REGULATIONS by temporarily reducing the price of a Licence to Possess Firearms, effective June 10, 2000, and by establishing a credit of $35 for those who paid the full price prior to that date, which may be used to offset the cost of renewing that Licence or for the issuance or renewal of a Possession & Acquisition Licence.
